full_text: Screened by NARA, 9/18/2023 UNITED STATES DEPARTMENT OF JUSTICE Form G-139 (Rev. 5/23/55) Immigration & Naturalization Service 70 Columbus Avenue Requesting Office Number File No. New York 23, N.Y. 0300 A10 090 167 G-JS (Address of requesting office) AR No. (If different than File No.) AGENCY ADDRESS CHECK REQUEST Date TO: April 16, 1956 SOCIAL SECURITY ADMINISTRATION THROUGH OFFICER IN CHARGE CHIEF, RECORDS ADMINISTRATION BRANCH CENTRAL OFFICE BALTIMORE, MD. The whereabouts of the alien named herein are being sought by this Service. It is requested that, in accordance with the provisions of section 290 of the Immigration and Nationality Act, all available information be furnished from your records which may be of assistancein establishing his location and identity. Indicate discrepancies, if any, and insert missing or more recent information, if available, on the face or reverse of this form.
